# Line-ending normalization. text=auto lets git detect text vs binary and store LF in the
# repo; Python and shell are pinned to LF in the working tree too, so a raw file md5 always
# equals the committed blob md5 and the S3 patchwork payload verification can never diverge
# on CRLF vs LF (fixes the 2026-07-05 deploy Step-0 HOLD).
* text=auto
*.py text eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
